09:36.353 --> 09:50.575
Appropriations Committee that first year was the 
little attention sometimes that is paid to riders

09:36.353 --> 09:50.575
that are placed in the appropriations bill. The 
new rider placed in the bill by a House member that

09:51.972 --> 10:11.922
